<i>adjective</i>: 틀림없다 [틀리멉따], 영락없다 [영나겁따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>틀림없다 [틀리멉따]</dt><br>
<dd>sure enough; invariably right; unfailing</dd><br>
<dd>조금도 틀리거나 어긋나는 일이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Absolutely correct, not wrong at all.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>영락없다 [영나겁따]</dt><br>
<dd>sure enough; invariably right; unfailing</dd><br>
<dd>조금도 틀리지 않고 꼭 들어맞다.</dd><br>
<dd>Absolutely correct, not wrong at all.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>